data.description: This charming 3-bedroom home features 1.75 baths, separate living and family rooms, and elegant tile flooring throughout. The spacious kitchen is perfect for entertaining, and the large fenced backyard with a screened covered patio offers a private outdoor retreat. With a double garage and walking distance to the grade school, this home is situated in a great Glendale neighborhood, making it an ideal choice for families. Storage unit on side of house. Owner will be putting a fresh coat of paint on in a few weeks.
